snippet.title: EAS Child Abduction Emergency (AMBER ALERT) Port Aurther, Texas KTXK-FM Texarkana/NOAA Weather Radio
snippet.description:
TXC005-037-063-067-073-159-183-203-315-343-347-365-387-401-403- 405-419-423-449-459-499-090300-

 BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE SHREVEPORT LA 653 PM CDT MON JUN 8 2020 

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT NETWORK THE PORT ARTHUR POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR JASON ROBERTS, BLACK, MALE, 7 MONTHS OLD, HEIGHT 2 FEET, WEIGHT 27 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR, BROWN EYES, AND LAST SEEN WEARING A GRAY ONESIE.

 POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR NATHAN LYNN ROBERTS JUNIOR, BLACK, MALE, 26 YEARS OLD, HEIGHT 5 FEET 10 INCHES, WEIGHT 178 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR, BROWN EYES AND LAST SEEN WEARING A BLACK MUSCLE SHIRT AND BLACK PANTS, IN CONNECTION WITH HIS ABDUCTION. 

THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A GOLD TAN JEEP CHEROKEE WITH AN UNKNOWN LICENSE PLATE. THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN PORT ARTHUR, TEXAS.

 LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR IMMEDIATE DANGER.

 IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE PORT ARTHUR POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 4 0 9 9 8 3 8 6 0 1.
